Version 0.2.1
-------------
- A new fallback backend for DPKG (Debian and derivatives)
- New configuration options (--enable-fallback-dpkg, --enable-fallback-rpm,
  --enable-fallback-all; --enable-fallback was dropped)
- Miscellaneous small fixes and cleanups

Version 0.2
-----------
- Added Extra Files metadata field (see psysmeta(7) man page)
- RPM fallback backend now checks if a package's LSB dependency is
  met (= if an installed package provides "lsb" in the required version)
- Miscellaneous small fixes

Version 0.1
-----------
- Initial version
- First revision of API for installing, updating, uninstalling
- Simple package metadata
- Basic RPM fallback backend
